Bring a large #pot{} of salted water to a boil. Wash and dry all produce. Trim and dice @zucchini{1} into ¼-inch pieces. Dice @cremini mushrooms{4%oz} into ¼-inch pieces. Dice @Roma tomato{1} into ¼-inch pieces. Halve, peel, and finely dice @yellow onion{1}.

Once water is boiling, add @spaghetti{6%oz} to pot and cook until al dente, ~{9-11%minutes}. Reserve 2 cups pasta cooking water, then drain.

Meanwhile, heat a large drizzle of @olive oil{} in a large #pan{} over medium-high heat. Add onion and cook until lightly browned, ~{3-4%minutes}. Add mushrooms and zucchini and cook until lightly browned and slightly softened, another ~{5-7%minutes}. Season generously with @salt{} and @pepper{}.

Add tomato, @tomato paste{3%tbsp}, @Italian seasoning{1%tbsp}, @garlic powder{3/4%tsp}, and a small pinch of @chili flakes{1%tsp} to pan. Cook, stirring, until thoroughly combined, ~{1-2%minutes}. Add @veggie stock concentrate{1} and 1 1/2 cups reserved pasta cooking water. Bring to a boil, then reduce heat to a simmer. Cook until thickened and veggies are soft, ~{7-8%minutes}.

Meanwhile, place @butter{2%tbsp} in a small #bowl{} and microwave until just softened, about ~{10%seconds} (do not melt). Stir in @Parmesan cheese{1%tbsp}, remaining @garlic powder{1/4%tsp}, a pinch of @salt{}, and a pinch of @chili flakes{} (to taste). Halve @demi-baguette{1} and toast until golden. Spread butter mixture onto cut sides of baguette, then halve on a diagonal.

Add spaghetti, @butter{1%tbsp}, and a splash of remaining pasta cooking water to sauce. Toss to combine, adding more pasta water as needed for sauce to fully coat pasta. Taste and season generously with salt and pepper. Divide finished pasta between bowls. Top with remaining Parmesan and a pinch of remaining chili flakes, if desired. Serve with garlic bread on the side.

> Some nights, nothing but a big bowl of pasta will do. This nourishing, veggie-loaded version is sure to curb the most ferocious carb cravings. Spaghetti is cloaked in a rich chili flake-spiked tomato sauce with tender bites of zucchini and meaty mushrooms.